data.description: Great 4 bedroom/2 full bath home with approx. 500 sq ft of fully finished basement with full bath in the village like community of Essex. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, parks and other recreational facilities. Enjoy entertaining on the large outdoor deck and side patio. Home also comes with playground quality swing set, storage unit. As well as a number of upgrades including a Ring motion detection cameras surrounding the entire perimeter, Delta touch faucet, One Link smoke detector, Phillips Hue Smart lights throughout the home, Glacier Bay full house water filtration system, high end stainless "smart" appliances, Eco-bee smart thermostat  and not to mention tons of charm. Located in a Boater's Community  just blocks away from Cox Point Park, on the Back River with huge  marina and boat launch You don't want to miss out on this one!
